export default function AssessmentForm() {
const [form, setForm] = useState({
name: "",
penalties: Array(10).fill(0),
bonus: ""
});

const baseScore = 50;
const totalPenalty = form.penalties.reduce((sum, val) => sum + Number(val), 0);
const totalScore = baseScore - totalPenalty + Number(form.bonus || 0);

const handlePenaltyChange = (index, value) => {
const updatedPenalties = [...form.penalties];
updatedPenalties[index] = value;
setForm({ ...form, penalties: updatedPenalties });
};
